Our Story

Building home away from home

Many Asian international students experience deep feelings of homesickness, loneliness, or cultural shock. Through Dragon 9, we vow to create a community where young souls can call home.

What started as an intramural soccer team has grown into something much greaterâ€”a movement dedicated to supporting the physical and mental wellbeing of international students at the University of Toronto. We believe that sports transcend language barriers and cultural differences, creating bonds that last a lifetime.

Our Vision

Grow from intramural team to enduring enterpriseâ€”multi-team, media-visible, sponsor-supported, and known for community and competitive standards.
